29 a passion for service and leadership, and growing up as the daughter of a
30 United States Marine Corps Colonel, she has a deep understanding of the
31 sacrifices military families make and a profound love for her country; and
32
33 WHEREAS, the multiple deployments of Peyton Bolling's father inspired
34 her to engage others in her community, promoting unity, civic participation,
35 and active citizenship; and
